                        <interp inst="t18530404-name-49" type="given" value="JOHN BARNETT"></interp>JOHN BARNETT RADLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I was going along St. Dunstan's-hill on 8th March—I did not miss anything till the officer told me—I then missed this handkerchief—I had it in my pocket ten minutes before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> This handkerchief hung out of his pocket; I took it to give it him; the officer seized me, and said I stole it.</p>
